{"name":"Shifter","type":"class","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><em>Shifters tap into magical power to alter their forms. They always seem to have the right solution for any problem, and they aren’t afraid to stand up to a foe. But they also study their enemies carefully to expand their shapeshifting.</em><br /><em>Shifters respect those whose forms they take, whether humanoid or monster, enemy or ally. With an empowered body and a strong personality, a shifter might be a powerhouse, a quick-footed precision striker, or a master of social graces.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Key Ability: STRENGTH, DEXTERITY, OR CHARISMA</strong></p>\n<p>At 1st level, your class gives you an ability boost to Strength, Dexterity or Charisma.</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points: 10 plus your Constitution modifier</strong></p>\n<p>You increase your maximum number of HP by this number at 1st level and every level thereafter.</p>\n<h1>Roleplaying the Shifter</h1>\n<h2>During Combat Encounters...</h2>\n<p>You adapt to the challenges presented to you by altering your form and tactics. Your allies likely know to give you a wide berth, and appreciate your ability to fill versatile roles on the battlefield</p>\n<h2>During Social Encounters...</h2>\n<p>You can take center stage or meld into the background as needed. You enhance your words with your visual appearance. You don’t always outright lie, but you definitely put the best face on, sometimes literally</p>\n<h2>While Exploring...</h2>\n<p>You might slide into difficult-to-reach places, or set up a perimeter defense, or befriend local creatures in their guise.</p>\n<h2>In Downtime...</h2>\n<p>You extensively study fallen enemies or willing allies to learn more about their forms.</p>\n<h2>You Might...</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have received your shapeshifting powers from magical experimentation, an eldritch source of power, or as a blessing from the gods or the forces of nature.</li>\n<li>Be open about your shifting nature or entrust this knowledge only to a select few.</li>\n<li>Find it easy to make acquaintances.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Others Probably...</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ask you incessant questions about your experiences in other forms.</li>\n<li>Request unusual tasks of you.</li>\n<li>Wonder about your true nature</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"shifter","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-07T21:31:20.185+04:00","version":{"schema":0.827,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.12.9"}}},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"keyAbility":{"value":["cha","dex","str"]},"items":{"Q9Ysn":{"uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.VgZIutWjFl8oZQFi","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/classes/expert-strikes.webp","name":"Expert Strikes","level":5},"OhkpW":{"uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.9EqIasqfI8YIM3Pt","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/classes/weapon-specialization.webp","name":"Weapon Specialization","level":7},"Oj6dX":{"uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.OMZs5y16jZRW9KQK","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/classes/juggerenaut.webp","name":"Juggernaut","level":9},"JuCIM":{"uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.MV6XIuAgN9uSA0Da","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/classes/evasion.webp","name":"Evasion","level":15},"VwkDM":{"uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.Z7HX6TeFsaup7Dx9","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/classes/greater-weapon-specialization.webp","name":"Greater Weapon Specialization","level":15},"ID65h":{"uuid":"Compendium.shifter-class.shifter-featsfeatures.8bMywqYayIcldgpS","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","name":"Shapeshifting","level":1},"c6jjM":{"uuid":"Compendium.shifter-class.shifter-featsfeatures.pr7W488EzQnx0Uy3","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","name":"Favored Form And Shifter Tradition","level":1},"EZuIx":{"uuid":"Compendium.shifter-class.shifter-featsfeatures.mOGx2gHDhT2yA2SQ","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","name":"Focus Points","level":1},"zW74r":{"uuid":"Compendium.shifter-class.shifter-